# LucidGate example list: weightedphraseexceptions
# Format: Weighted phrase syntax is <phrase><weight>. The score threshold is configured in TOML as semantic.score_threshold.
# Lines beginning with # are comments and are ignored by the loader.
# To activate a rule, copy one example, remove the leading # and adapt it to your environment.
# You can include another file with: .Include<relative-or-absolute-path>
#
# Commented examples:
# <credential dump><80>
# <private api key><70>
# <internal admin password><90>
# <malware staging url><60>
# <phishing landing page><60>
# <exploit kit marker><70>
# <password reset token><50>
# <confidential roadmap><30>
# <secret signing key><90>
# <production database dump><90>
